<% provide(:title, 'Rules') %>
<div id="rules">
	<h1>Rules and Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
	<div id="main-rules" class="inner-shadow">
	<p>Pick at least one game a week with the following extras:
		<ul>
			<li>Take a mandatory BYE once during the season</li>
			<li>5 "wildcards" or game multipliers</li>
		</ul>
	</p>
	</div>

	<h2>Picks</h2>
	<div class="rules-list">
		<dl>
		<dt>How is my score calculated when I pick a game?</dt>
		<dd class style="overflow: hidden; display: none;">
			<%= image_tag(image_path('pick-ex1.png')) %>
			<p>Using the spread above.  If you pick the favorite, you subtract 3.5 points from the final score.  If you pick the underdog, you add 3.5 points to the final score.
			<br/>Picking the Favorite: <span class="positive-num">Favorite Score</span> - <span class="negative-num">(Underdog Score <b>+ Spread</b>)</span>
			<br/>Picking the Underdog: <span class="positive-num">(Favorite Score - <b class="negative-num">Spread</b>)</span> - <span class="negative-num">Underdog Score</p>
		</dd>
		<dt>Can I submit a pick through email, phone, or in-person?</dt>
		<dd class style="overflow: hidden; display: none;">
			<p>No, all picks must be submitted through the website.</p>
		</dd>
		<dt>When do I have to submit my pick by?</dt>
		<dd class style="overflow: hidden; display: none;">
			<p>All picks must be submitted before the first game on Sunday.  Picks for the Thursday game must be submitted before the kickoff of Thursday.</p>
		</dd>
		<dt>What happens if I do not submit a pick?</dt>
		<dd class style="overflow: hidden; display: none;">
			<p>If no pick is submitted by the first game of Sunday, you will be given the HOME TEAM of the last played game of the week.</p>
		</dd>
		<dt>How does the BYE work?</dt>
		<dd class style="overflow: hidden; display: none;">
			<ul>
				<li>You only have <u>ONE</u> BYE per season.</li>
				<li>A BYE indicates that no game will be picked for that week.</li>
				<li>If you do not use your BYE before the last week of the season.  Your BYE will be applied to the last week.</li>
			</ul>
		</dd>
		<dt>How do Wildcards work?</dt>
		<dd class style="overflow: hidden; display: none;">
			<ul>
				<li>Every player has a total of <b><u>5</b></u> wildcards per season.</li>
				<li>A wildcard can be used to pick an additional game per week. When choosing to do this, the wildcard will be applied automatically and no manual specification is required.</li>
				<li>A wildcard may be used as a multiplier for the points gained.  For example, if you win by 10pts and applied 1 wildcard to your pick.  You would have a total of 20pts (10pts x 2).</li>
				<li>You do not have to use all of your wildcards.</li>
			</ul>
		</dd>
		</dl>
	</div>
	<br>
	<h2>Playoffs</h2>
	<div class="rules-list">
		<div class="rules-section">
			<dt>Do we pick playoff games too?</dt>
			<dd class style="overflow: hidden; display: none;">
				<p>Yes and no. There are playoffs in this league, but you qualify based on your total score in the regular season.</p>
			</dd>
			<dt>What is the criteria for qualifying for the playoffs?</td>
			<dd class style="overflow: hidden; display: none;">
				<p>You must satisfy one of these criteria to make the playoffs:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>One of the top 10 point earners</li>
					<li>Bottom 2 point earners</li>
				</ul>
			</dd>
		</div>
	</div>
	<br/>
	<h2>Payouts</h2>
	<div class="rules-list">
		<dt>What is the entry fee?</dt>
		<dd class style="overflow: hidden; display: none;">
			<p>Entry fee is $150.</p>
		</dd>
		<dt>What are the payouts?</dt>
		<dd class style="overflow: hidden; display: none;">
			<p>Regular Season accounts for 70% and Playoffs account for 30%.</p>
				<div id="rounded-corner">
					<div class="rounded-corner-table left">
						<div class="rounded-corner-head"><div>Regular Season</div><div>&nbsp;</div></div>
						<div class="rounded-corner-head"><div>Place</div><div>Payout %</div></div>
						<div class="rounded-corner-row"><div>1</div><div>16.0%</div></div>
						<div class="rounded-corner-row"><div>2</div><div>12.0%</div></div>
						<div class="rounded-corner-row"><div>3</div><div>9.5%</div></div>
						<div class="rounded-corner-row"><div>4</div><div>7.0%</div></div>
						<div class="rounded-corner-row"><div>5</div><div>6.0%</div></div>
						<div class="rounded-corner-row"><div>6-10</div><div>3.48%</div></div>
						<div class="rounded-corner-foot"><div>*Payouts have not been finalized</div><div>&nbsp;</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="rounded-corner-table right">
						<div class="rounded-corner-head"><div>Playoffs</div><div>&nbsp;</div></div>
						<div class="rounded-corner-head"><div>Place</div><div>Payout %</div></div>
						<div class="rounded-corner-row"><div>1</div><div>50.0%</div></div>
						<div class="rounded-corner-row"><div>2</div><div>33.0%</div></div>
						<div class="rounded-corner-row"><div>3</div><div>17.0%</div></div>
						<div class="rounded-corner-foot"><div>*Payouts have not been finalized</div><div>&nbsp;</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</dd>
		<dt>How do we submit our entry fee?</dt>
		<dd class style="overflow: hidden; display: none;">
			<p>Paypal mother fucker! Do you use it!?!?!</p>
		</dd>
	</div>
</div>